name: Um SER distante
description:
This sculpture work is a study of forms, movements, expressions and human figures.

In a free and spontaneous way I mold the sculpture without knowing what I will get at the end of the modeling, faces I have never seen, someone's features and distinct facial expressions.

Sculpture in plastic clay.
size of the sculpture: 9 cm.
